Thereâ€™s now a single source of truth for the Health Cloud Admin Guide in Salesforce Help. Previously, the guide was available on both the Salesforce help site and developer.salesforce.com/docs.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions.

Why: We wanted to provide a single location for you to access the guide.

How: Navigate to Salesforce Help (help.salesforce.com) and click View all products. Then click the product tile for Health Cloud and look for Administer Health Cloud.

Salesforce Help: Administer Health Cloud
title: Single Source of Truth for Health Cloud Admin Guide
